source.title: Anglo-Saxon Chronicles
source.editorial-note: The text was imported from the York-Toronto-Helsinki Parsed Corpus of Old English Prose (YCOE), including the morphological annotation. Further morphological annotation was then added, including lemmatization. The syntactic annotation is independent of YCOE. Documentation for the morphological and syntactic annotation can be found here: http://folk.uio.no/krisbec/OE_guidelines.pdf
source.electronic-text-editor: Ann Taylor, Anthony Warner, Susan Pintzuk, Frank Beths
